{"TopicId":163346,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.9.x - 1.12.x] Fox Defense Contracts - Tank Turrets (BDArmory Plus) Update 2.1 Add More Duct Tape","CreatedByName":"lancefoxcia","CreatedById":10699,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-17T05:43:21Z","PageNum":3,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dimas152","CreatedById":179714,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-26T12:26:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223252223\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221514164870\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210699\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lancefoxcia\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/25/2017 at 8:21 AM, lancefoxcia said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe oerlikon cannon is a 30mm cannon. for sure the T-34-85 turret is going to be bigger.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe IS turret was pretty much the T-34-85\u0027s turret in real life.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni compared both\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022wYcdpn9.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wYcdpn9.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBT-7 is ok, but the T-34/85 looks kinda oversized, even A\u00A0little bit smaller than NAS naval guns\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\ncomparison\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qZ1CIdW.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022575\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qZ1CIdW.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-12-26T12:34:59Z\u0022 title=\u002212/26/2017 12:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 26, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by [INDO]dimas_1502\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dimas152","CreatedById":179714,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-26T12:49:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\noh wait NAS seems oversized too\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Acea","CreatedById":98766,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-26T13:25:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223253021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221514292546\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022[INDO]dimas_1502\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n44 minutes ago, [INDO]dimas_1502 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\noh wait NAS seems oversized too\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNAS is using real world values, it\u0027s \u003Cstrong\u003Esome\u003C/strong\u003E BDAc parts which are smaller than real weapons.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: All right not all of them, but quite a number of guns are scaled down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XOC2008","CreatedById":151259,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-26T13:31:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223253032\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221514294749\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298766\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Acea\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Acea said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNAS is using real world values, it\u0027s \u003Cstrong\u003Esome\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003EBDAc parts which are smaller than real weapons.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFixed that for you. While BDAc sizes are a bit all over the place, a lot of weapons in there like the missiles and bombs are close enough to real world values as far as sizes to be considered accurate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dimas152","CreatedById":179714,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-26T14:12:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso \u0022not-so\u0022 kerbal sized?\u003Cbr\u003E\ni see\u003Cbr\u003E\njust hope tweakscale can rescale these\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lancefoxcia","CreatedById":10699,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-26T20:00:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223253057\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221514297559\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022[INDO]dimas_1502\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, [INDO]dimas_1502 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso \u0022not-so\u0022 kerbal sized?\u003Cbr\u003E\ni see\u003Cbr\u003E\njust hope tweakscale can rescale these\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTweakscale will cause sorts of problems with Bdac content. I\u0027d suggest going into the cfg files for the weapons and look at the rescale_weapons part and scale to your liking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother thing to point out is that there\u0027 no universal scaling for the weapons we make so we just try to either eyeball it or use our own way. Some weapons may be bigger then others but it\u0027 something that might take a long time to fix since it\u0027l have to be all the bdac creators to work together to create a scale for the weapons\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal Nerd123","CreatedById":165626,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-03T15:07:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill waiting for that Bumbar....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-03T17:10:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223284752\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221517670460\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165626\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbal Nerd123\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Kerbal Nerd123 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill waiting for that Bumbar....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKeep waiting\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HunHarcos","CreatedById":177007,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-15T20:30:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice updates you have made to the mod. A question. Im still using 1.2.2, and I am using the modpack provided by BeardyPenguin. Can I use the latest version of your mod with my game, plus keeping the values and turrets modified by Beardy? Plus having your new turrets(russians) as well?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lancefoxcia","CreatedById":10699,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-15T20:51:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223296002\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518726642\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177007\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HunHarcos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, HunHarcos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice updates you have made to the mod. A question. Im still using 1.2.2, and I am using the modpack provided by BeardyPenguin. Can I use the latest version of your mod with my game, plus keeping the values and turrets modified by Beardy? Plus having your new turrets(russians) as well?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell this version of FDC uses the new version of BDAc 1.0\u003Cbr\u003E\nHowever I can simply get the weapons ready for 1.2.2 for you. Won\u0027t take long and I\u0027ll post here with the download for you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223284752\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221517670460\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165626\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbal Nerd123\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/3/2018 at 10:07 AM, Kerbal Nerd123 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill waiting for that Bumbar....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s coming. College is the main reason i\u0027m not able to add in more stuff.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dimas152","CreatedById":179714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-03T03:43:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nno updates so far? maybe i can help for texturing\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nalso, maybe u can use NKD\u0027s KV-2 turret for scaling reference, it\u0027s a bit smaller than ur KV-2 turret\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PossiblyPrecarious","CreatedById":187541,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T04:36:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso is this gonna be made for 1.4.X?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lancefoxcia","CreatedById":10699,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T04:45:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223372064\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525581418\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187541\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PossiblyPrecarious\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, PossiblyPrecarious said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso is this gonna be made for 1.4.X?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u