n-beta version 1.4 compatible too?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lancefoxcia","CreatedById":10699,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-09T06:36:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223374241\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525818251\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165701\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sidestrafe2462\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Sidestrafe2462 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ngotcha\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncan you make the non-beta version 1.4 compatible too?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe non-beta is just made for BDAc\u00A01.0 which is no longer a thing as 1.1-1.2 took over. I\u0027m fixing the mod description up right now.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dimas152","CreatedById":179714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-09T11:22:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223253310\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221514318400\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210699\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lancefoxcia\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/27/2017 at 3:00 AM, lancefoxcia said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother thing to point out is that there\u0027 no universal scaling for the weapons we make so we just try to either eyeball it or use our own way. Some weapons may be bigger then others but it\u0027 something that might take a long time to fix since it\u0027l have to be all the bdac creators to work together to create a scale for the weapons\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlong time no see lul\u003Cbr\u003E\njust rescale the model in unity maybe?\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nalso it seems that the stock BDAc\u0027s abrams turret is kerbal sized\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XOC2008","CreatedById":151259,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-09T11:43:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRegarding scale: Most of the SM hulls and turrets are at or are near scale, so you could base a fair amount of your scaling off of those.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PossiblyPrecarious","CreatedById":187541,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T14:43:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you going to fix up the turrets for the newest version of BDA cuz the bullets work differently and now the bullets in FDC don\u0027t work\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}